# Jokula Design Agency Minimal: Source of Truth

> **Design Philosophy:** Minimalist design agency portfolio with focus on visual storytelling and clean typography.

This document serves as the definitive guide for recreating the design aesthetic of **Jokula**, a design agency website. Every design decision, component specification, and interaction pattern is documented here to ensure consistency across implementations.

