## PHASE 3: RESPONSIVE DESIGN

### Breakpoints

**Mobile First Approach:**
- **Mobile:** `0px - 767px`
- **Tablet:** `768px - 1023px`
- **Desktop:** `1024px+`
- **Large Desktop:** `1440px+`

**Implementation:**
```css
/* Mobile (default) */
.container {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
}

/* Tablet */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
}

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 4rem;
  }
}

/* Large Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1440px) {
